The paper deals with video summarization, which involves analyzing and summarizing video content. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of semantic information to guide the summarization process, which involves natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper involves the use of subset selection techniques, which is a common topic in information retrieval (cs.IR).
